cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.CY, cs.AI, cs.IR 

This paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning techniques to extract patient conditions from clinical notes. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses neural language models, which suggests that it could be classified under cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with healthcare data, which could fall under cs.CY (Computers and Society). The use of contextualized language models also suggests that the paper could be classified under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper deals with information retrieval from medical records, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
